{"parentUuid":"090d9698-c006-46a8-878d-2bfb240b0224","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"8a0970a7-992a-482d-b1fb-9fa84d4f1b3d","agentId":"acecf48983d445221","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MubK1F39rwuZPAJcu3qp7t","type":"tool_result","content":"On branch feature/metric-quotas\nChanges not staged for commit:\n  (use \"git add <file>...\" to update what will be committed)\n  (use \"git restore <file>...\" to discard changes in working directory)\n\tmodified:   .claude/settings.json\n\tmodified:   .github/workflows/pipeline-ci.yml\n\tmodified:   CLAUDE.md\n\tmodified:   PROJECT.md\n\tmodified:   alembic/README.md\n\tmodified:   docs/system_architecture.md\n\tmodified:   scripts/README.md\n\tmodified:   scripts/ci/dast-review.sh\n\tmodified:   scripts/ci/guard-source-markers.sh\n\tmodified:   scripts/seed_api_key.py\n\tmodified:   src/api/README.md\n\tmodified:   src/api/errors.py\n\tmodified:   src/api/middleware.py\n\tmodified:   src/auth/README.md\n\tmodified:   src/auth/api_key.py\n\tmodified:   src/db/README.md\n\tmodified:   src/db/session.py\n\tmodified:   src/main.py\n\tmodified:   src/repositories/README.md\n\tmodified:   src/repositories/api_keys_repo.py\n\tmodified:   src/services/README.md\n\tmodified:   src/services/events_service.py\n\tmodified:   tests/integration/conftest.py\n\tmodified:   tests/integration/test_perf_k6_load.py\n\tmodified:   tests/integration/test_seed_api_key_script.py\n\nUntracked files:\n  (use \"git add <file>...\" to include in what will be committed)\n\t.claude/skills/ast-grep-rules/\n\talembic/versions/0003_create_quotas_and_api_key_scope.py\n\tdocs/decisions/feature/\n\tsrc/api/routes/quotas.py\n\tsrc/api/schemas/quotas.py\n\tsrc/repositories/quotas_repo.py\n\tsrc/services/quota_service.py\n\ttests/README.md\n\ttests/integration/README.md\n\ttests/integration/k6/README.md\n\ttests/integration/k6/load_events_quota.js\n\ttests/integration/test_events_quota_enforcement.py\n\ttests/integration/test_quota_concurrency.py\n\ttests/integration/test_quota_migration.py\n\ttests/integration/test_quotas_endpoint.py\n\ttests/integration/test_quotas_rls_backstop.py\n\ttests/test_db_session_isolation.py\n\ttests/test_schemas_quotas.py\n\nno changes added to commit (use \"git add\" and/or \"git commit -a\")\n=====DIFF STAT=====\n .claude/settings.json                         |  54 +++++-\n .github/workflows/pipeline-ci.yml             |  28 ++++\n CLAUDE.md                                     |   4 +-\n PROJECT.md                                    |  49 +-----\n alembic/README.md                             |   8 +\n docs/system_architecture.md                   | 100 +++++++++--\n scripts/README.md                             |   8 +-\n scripts/ci/dast-review.sh                     |  19 ++-\n scripts/ci/guard-source-markers.sh            |  38 +++--\n scripts/seed_api_key.py                       |  17 +-\n src/api/README.md                             |  11 +-\n src/api/errors.py                             |  26 ++-\n src/api/middleware.py                         |   2 +-\n src/auth/README.md                            |   7 +-\n src/auth/api_key.py                           |  13 +-\n src/db/README.md                              |   9 +\n src/db/session.py                             |   9 +\n src/main.py                                   |   2 +\n src/repositories/README.md                    |  12 +-\n src/repositories/api_keys_repo.py             |  14 +-\n src/services/README.md                        |  20 ++-\n src/services/events_service.py                |  54 +++++-\n tests/integration/conftest.py                 |  25 ++-\n tests/integration/test_perf_k6_load.py        | 228 +++++++++++++++++++++++++-\n tests/integration/test_seed_api_key_script.py |  42 +++++\n 25 files changed, 687 insertions(+), 112 deletions(-)","is_error":false}]},"uuid":"8325a74d-460f-4116-bb08-753f2bc868c5","timestamp":"2026-07-09T03:58:30.923Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"090d96